<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Effusion" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Effusion,</orth> 1) shedding, spilling: <cit><quote>of blood,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.138" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 138</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 1, 9</bibl>. <cit><quote>of tears,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 2, 49</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) that which is poured out: (thy children) <cit><quote>the mere e. of thy proper loins,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 30</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>